cs_greece
---------

Map for Counter-Strike : Source

Installation
------------
Extract cs_greece.bsp, cs_greece.nav and cs_greece.txt for you maps directory,
usually C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\Your name\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps

Have fun playing it !


For further informations, contact naar-shilka@bluewin.ch
